These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, social-worker
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, photography
2 different games are played: scrabble, snooker
1. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the musician is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Job           | social-worker | musician |
| Hobby   | traveling       | photography  |
| Game     | scrabble      | snooker     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, daisy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, r&b
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, sudoku
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Flower          | daisy | marigold |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | r&b         |
| Hobby           | sudoku     | woodworking         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
House: townhouse, palace
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the townhouse house##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| House           | palace | townhouse     |
| Beverage   | cola            | soy-milk         |
| Transport     | scooter         | quad-bike   |

