.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, weightlifting
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: hamster, rat
1. the australian is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
2. the person drinking tea is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | rugby |
| Nationality   | australian   | pakistani |
| Pet           | hamster | rat    |

