2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite    | mirinda |
| Birthday       | august | november  |
| Hobby      | skydiving | hiking  |
| Color        | pink  | grey    |

