The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, tennis
There are 2 different nationalities: american, british
2 different pets are kept: bird, pony
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the american##1
2. the british is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Game         | canasta | snooker |
| Sport           | tennis     | badminton |
| Nationality   | american      | british    |
| Pet           | pony          | bird       |

