.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-17::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, punk
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, lilac
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, surfing
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who likes black##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | quad-bike |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | funk      |
| Color   | lilac | black   |
| Sport         | surfing  | badminton |

