.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
There are 2 different nationalities: german, russian
2 different games are played: canasta, billiard
1. the russian is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the german##1
3. the german is the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk     | iced-tea |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Nationality   | russian     | german     |
| Game     | canasta | billiard     |

 